<a id="5"><hr></a>
<h3>5. Download results</h3>
<p> The user is notified by an email, as soon as the imputation job has finished. A zip archive including the results can be downloaded directly from the server. To decrypt the results, a one-time password is generated by the server and included in the email. The data is deleted automatically after <b>3</b> days.
The QC report can be displayed and downloaded as well.</p>
